'''谢丽尔·布恩·伊萨克斯'''（{{lang-en|Cheryl Boone Isaacs}}，{{bd|1949年||}}），美国{{le|电影营销|Film promotion}}和[[公关|公关]]高层人员。她曾代表凭借一年一度的[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]闻名的[[美国电影艺术与科学学院|美国电影艺术与科学学院]]公关部，出任学院理事会理事。截至2013年，她已担任该职长达21年之久。2013年7月30日，她获选为学院第35任主席<ref name=AMPAS-President-2013>{{cite web|last1=Melidonian|first1=Teni|url=http://www.oscars.org/news/cheryl-boone-isaacs-elected-academy-president|title=Cheryl Boone Isaacs Elected Academy President|work=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences|date=2013-07-30|accessdate=2013-08-02|archive-date=2014-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015120358/http://www.oscars.org/news/cheryl-boone-isaacs-elected-academy-president|dead-url=no}}</ref>。伊萨克斯是该职位的首位[[非裔美国人|非裔美国人]]和继[[贝蒂·戴维斯|贝蒂·戴维斯]]和{{le|费·卡宁|Fay Kanin}}之后的第三位女性<ref name=GoldDerby-AMPAS-President-2013>{{cite web|last=Gold Derby News Desk|url=http://www.goldderby.com/news/4617/cheryl-boone-isaacs-oscars-ampas-film-news-13579086.html|title=Cheryl Boone Isaacs elected first African-American head of Oscars|work=Gold Derby|date=2013-07-31|accessdate=2013-08-02|archive-date=2013-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130804084056/http://www.goldderby.com/news/4617/cheryl-boone-isaacs-oscars-ampas-film-news-13579086.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=HReporter-AMPAS-President-2013>{{cite news|last1=Kilday|first1=Gregg|title=New Academy President Cheryl Boone Isaacs on Her Historic Election, the Oscars and Her Top Priorities (Q&A)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/new-academy-president-cheryl-boone-597239|accessdate=2015-11-15|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2013-07-31|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117064554/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/new-academy-president-cheryl-boone-597239|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

